             Date: Wed, 04 Jun 2003 00:08:32 -0700
             Message-ID: <wrZ3+gzkg2iX092yn@efn.org>
             
             [ 19696]
             Perl *is* 100% 64bit compliant on HP-UX 11.00 and up (as long
             as the compiler supports it)
             
             [ 19697]
             Oops, Joe's edits had been undone by #19682.
             
