[ 19653] By: jhi                                   on 2003/06/01  07:35:55
        Log: Integrate:
             [ 19638]
             Comment tweakage.
             
             [ 19639]
             Add the test case for the already fixed
             [perl #22351] perl bug with 'e' substitution modifier
             
             [ 19640]
             Fix for "#22375 'split'/'index' problem for utf8".
             
             [ 19641]
